01:23:44,158 --> 01:23:46,150
Tell me what happened. It's all right.

1197
01:23:53,168 --> 01:23:54,875
Did you sleep with her?

1198
01:23:57,923 --> 01:23:58,836
No.

1199
01:23:59,342 --> 01:24:02,841
