1200
01:24:09,853 --> 01:24:11,810
I am so disappointed in you.

1201
01:24:14,609 --> 01:24:18,358
I know you feel like shit now,
but I'm not gonna lie to you.

1202
01:24:18,571 --> 01:24:23,448
You compromised yourself,
our relationship and Lance and Mia's.

1203
01:24:25,997 --> 01:24:27,029
I know.

1204
01:24:29,376 --> 01:24:30,953
I'm glad you told me.

1205
01:24:33,631 --> 01:24:35,789
At least now I know
where I stand with you.

1206
01:24:35,883 --> 01:24:39,299
- No, baby. You know that is not true.
- Don't!

1207
01:24:41,473 --> 01:24:43,799
I may not be perfect, but I'm strong.

1208
01:24:51,109 --> 01:24:53,862
I hope you can make this right.
The wedding starts soon.

1209
01:24:53,946 --> 01:24:54,977
How?

1210
01:24:56,741 --> 01:25:00,406
I've been lookin' all over for Lance,
and I cannot find him.

1211
01:25:01,204 --> 01:25:06,163
