1215
01:25:29,653 --> 01:25:31,362
I cannot do this alone.

1216
01:25:34,701 --> 01:25:36,611
Please don't leave me now.

1217
01:25:46,923 --> 01:25:48,631
Okay, I'll go with you.

1218
01:25:49,343 --> 01:25:53,009
